Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.01,0:00:03.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fad(300,600)}{\fs40}艾利斯家 庭园
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.04,0:00:12.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么 你还活着啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.48,0:00:14.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这招呼打的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.47,0:00:15.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没听说传闻吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.34,0:00:19.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在我可是小有名气的英雄了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.57,0:00:20.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没听过
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.63,0:00:21.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你怎么在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.35,0:00:24.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是艾利斯家请我来的啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.01,0:00:28.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我请他来的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.10,0:00:31.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兄长
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.32,0:00:34.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,初次见面 席恩·阿斯塔尔君
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.53,0:00:38.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是艾利斯家的主人 露西尔·艾利斯
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.83,0:00:47.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今日请你来不为他事
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.00,0:00:51.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是想听听你的想法
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.70,0:00:53.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的想法？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.93,0:00:56.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我现在将问你几个问题
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.07,0:01:00.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这些问题是为了判断你是否有资格
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.50,0:01:02.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希望你能回答我
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.54,0:01:06.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过在提问之前 我有一个条件
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.01,0:01:09.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,若你的答案不能令人满意
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.14,0:01:11.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我便杀了你
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.84,0:01:15.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放心 不会有痛苦
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.73,0:01:19.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你甚至不会感觉到自己的脑袋和身体分了家
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.37,0:01:23.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的表情似乎觉得难以理解
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.62,0:01:26.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过 这里可是艾利斯家
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.72,0:01:28.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,席恩·阿斯塔尔
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.58,0:01:32.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来如此
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.15,0:01:35.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,代代只侍奉王者的家门之主
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.75,0:01:37.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想要试探我
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.14,0:01:40.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本国的始祖 阿斯路德·罗兰德的末裔
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.06,0:01:42.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全部拥有这种资格
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.75,0:01:45.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即便是下贱的狗杂种
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.86,0:01:48.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吧 我就听听你的问题
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.43,0:01:50.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说吧 露西尔·艾利斯
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.11,0:01:53.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就知道你会这么说
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.22,0:01:55.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,随我来
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.85,0:01:58.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无聊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.14,0:02:00.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好不容易从战场捡回来的命
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.51,0:02:01.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打算扔在这里吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.67,0:02:06.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好不容易捡回来的命更应如此

Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.10,0:03:45.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fad(300,600)}{\fs40}罗兰德 城下城区
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.04,0:03:53.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让开让开
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.88,0:03:56.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,公爵大人要过路了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.02,0:04:04.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fad(300,0)}{\fs40}罗兰德 高等收监所
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.99,0:04:10.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天能早点回来吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.91,0:04:13.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行 有新来的囚犯
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.16,0:04:16.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在他习惯之前暂时得晚点回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.70,0:04:17.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.06,0:04:20.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道他干了什么 真可怜
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.96,0:04:24.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,进了这里可就永不见天日了嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.76,0:04:28.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下次出来时怕就是…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.18,0:04:29.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是年轻人吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.58,0:04:32.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 还不满20的样子
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.13,0:04:35.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大叔 看守大叔
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.05,0:04:38.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天又怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.13,0:04:40.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思 你提再多次
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.55,0:04:43.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fad(300,600)}{\fs40}莱纳·报告
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.00,0:04:44.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也不能给你高级棉被或者羽毛被什么的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.77,0:04:51.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了 你今天又想要什么
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.72,0:04:54.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,纸和铅笔 还有
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.01,0:04:57.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是有个王立军事特殊学院吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.48,0:05:00.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希望你从那里的图书馆帮我借点书来
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.42,0:05:02.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,书啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.42,0:05:06.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这点东西倒是无所谓
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.10,0:05:07.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.18,0:05:09.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加起来大概30本左右
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.00,0:05:12.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,3、30本？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.03,0:05:24.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然在这里织网
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.13,0:05:26.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你活不活得下去啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.07,0:05:30.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里可是连只苍蝇都没有的牢房啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.54,0:05:37.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是这么硬…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.99,0:05:48.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来 分你一点
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.56,0:05:50.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给你拿来了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.54,0:05:54.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多谢啦 大叔
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.88,0:06:00.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你收集这么多书 每天都在干嘛呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.39,0:06:03.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有 不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.63,0:06:06.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能不能麻烦你再加借个10本左右？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.20,0:06:08.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊？还不够啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.64,0:06:22.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么 还没睡啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.77,0:06:27.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你可真是个怪人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.85,0:06:30.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一般人在这昏暗诡异的环境下
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.80,0:06:32.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早就神经错乱了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.99,0:06:36.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多闹腾的家伙 过个一星期都会变得沉默寡言
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.11,0:06:39.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,过一个月大都…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.40,0:06:47.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是个怪人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.60,0:06:58.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哟 这是今天的份
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.18,0:06:59.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 3Q
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.63,0:07:03.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,王立特殊学院之后是阿斯路德纪念图书馆吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.72,0:07:07.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,该不会过阵子全国的图书馆都搬这儿来了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.11,0:07:11.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你家闺女 感冒好了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.27,0:07:13.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 活蹦乱跳的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.36,0:07:14.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有你听我说啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.96,0:07:17.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她终于能自己站起来走路了哟
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.85,0:07:20.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的吗 那可真棒啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.16,0:07:23.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀 一想到这孩子终于也长这么大了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.16,0:07:25.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就感动得不行
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.11,0:07:28.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小孩子长起来真是不等人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.22,0:07:30.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过是刚会走路而已 说什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.74,0:07:34.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在就这样 等到她长大成人出嫁那一天…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.66,0:07:37.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种事绝不容许
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.94,0:07:41.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你该不是看上我家闺女了吧 是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.74,0:07:42.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么会这样
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.02,0:07:44.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冷静点啦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.99,0:07:48.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我得加油了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.30,0:07:52.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 我想等大叔的闺女长大时
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.70,0:07:56.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是还有战争 你也不乐意吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.31,0:07:57.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那当然
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.48,0:08:01.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,世上哪有父母会心甘情愿送子女上战场的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.84,0:08:02.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说得也是
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.16,0:08:06.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,战争到底是不行啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.57,0:08:19.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大叔 今天好香啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.04,0:08:21.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,闻出来了？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.04,0:08:25.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天稍微奢侈点 是蒜蓉鸡肉吉士烤三明治
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.65,0:08:29.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可是每天都得忍受淡得跟水一样的汤哎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.73,0:08:32.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最近老婆生意做得好
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.32,0:08:34.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人还是要吃肉啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.31,0:08:38.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大叔你家两口子都挣钱啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.54,0:08:41.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 老婆在早市帮人卖蔬菜
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.46,0:08:45.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其实有吃奶的孩子 真不想让她去干活的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.13,0:08:48.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过 总比当兵好
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.89,0:08:51.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,七年前有场大战吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.41,0:08:53.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当时我也在军队里
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.53,0:08:56.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被拉上战场 伙伴们都死了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.32,0:09:00.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我实在是受够战争了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.93,0:09:02.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.46,0:09:06.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我辞了队长的官 来了这里
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.92,0:09:09.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然生活苦了点 不过我不后悔
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.62,0:09:11.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.35,0:09:21.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来来 好高好高
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.70,0:09:42.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来如此
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.09,0:09:49.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就是你所选择的道路吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.15,0:09:53.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以为能在这里永远午睡下去
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.61,0:09:54.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可就大错特错了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.50,0:10:19.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你还真是够古怪的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.13,0:10:25.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪儿不比这里亮堂多粮好过活啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.66,0:10:27.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,干嘛老待在这儿不走呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.07,0:10:46.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,惨 还以为要窒息了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.72,0:10:49.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看样子再不整理一下真要死了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.25,0:10:52.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 总之先吃个早饭
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.91,0:10:55.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,睡个回笼觉之后再慢慢整
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.96,0:11:00.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 正等你呢大叔
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.32,0:11:01.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天的饭…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.41,0:11:05.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大叔 怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.25,0:11:08.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出什么事了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.23,0:11:14.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吧 又和老婆吵架了？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.26,0:11:17.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是闺女介绍男朋友给你了所以很失落？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.93,0:11:21.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,胡说八道 我闺女才三岁啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.16,0:11:23.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在的三岁小孩可牛了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.18,0:11:24.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不知道吗大叔
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.83,0:11:28.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你你你是说哪方面牛 我家闺女可不会…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.55,0:11:30.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,每个家长都是这么说的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.54,0:11:32.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是啦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.70,0:11:36.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是啦 不是因为这些…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.48,0:11:39.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么事啦 真是
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.00,0:11:41.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,话说我的早饭呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.07,0:11:49.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.35,0:11:50.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算了 不用说了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.50,0:11:54.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就那啥 我的死刑定了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.66,0:11:59.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这国家总算养怪物养怕了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.59,0:12:03.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也罢 放我多活了差不多两年
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.00,0:12:05.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也该谢天谢地了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.08,0:12:08.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了 大叔
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.97,0:12:11.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在这里写的研究报告
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.28,0:12:12.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能一起带走吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.31,0:12:17.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个…命令书上说禁止带任何东西
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.75,0:12:19.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.58,0:12:23.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算了 马上要死的人也不需要那玩意儿了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.31,0:12:28.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别哭丧着脸了 大叔
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.54,0:12:29.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.67,0:12:40.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走了 你保重
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.04,0:12:53.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莱纳你去哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.93,0:12:58.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莱纳拜拜
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.44,0:13:21.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他就是莱纳·琉特吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.92,0:13:30.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我去了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.97,0:13:32.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诸事承蒙照顾了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.60,0:13:42.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说这位美女
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.54,0:13:45.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么事色情狂
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.16,0:13:52.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃…那啥
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.83,0:13:56.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不介意的话能不能问问您为什么叫我色情狂？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.77,0:13:57.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为脸
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.65,0:14:00.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有经历
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.15,0:14:02.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的事我听说了不少
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.75,0:14:04.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.56,0:14:07.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思 我要在这里逃掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.72,0:14:09.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 竟想和我打吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.39,0:14:12.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以前跟人约好了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.31,0:14:14.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我还不能死
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.74,0:14:16.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吾所求雷鸣
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.41,0:14:17.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,电光
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.54,0:14:29.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,开 开玩笑吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.89,0:14:33.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伤脑筋
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.46,0:14:35.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这下我不动真格的怕是真要死在她手里了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.07,0:14:38.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 这么说刚才那下不是真格的了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.32,0:14:42.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 也就七成功力吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.48,0:14:44.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来如此 怪不得那家伙想要
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.02,0:14:47.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.13,0:14:49.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等暂停
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.21,0:14:52.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吾献上契约之文 寄宿沉眠于大地的恶意之精兽
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.55,0:15:12.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.65,0:15:14.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然能跟上这魔法
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.37,0:15:15.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是用了什么法术…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.33,0:15:21.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有？什么也没？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.12,0:15:24.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用任何魔法还能这样
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.28,0:15:25.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可能
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.46,0:15:29.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吾所求水云
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.80,0:15:30.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,崩雨
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.06,0:15:48.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你刚才手下留情了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.96,0:15:50.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么这么想
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.73,0:15:51.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚才的魔法
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.98,0:15:55.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果不用水而用可大范围攻击的火炎魔法
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.98,0:15:58.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就有可能击中我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.63,0:16:01.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃 但是那样你说不定会死嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.02,0:16:05.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难得这么漂亮的脸蛋 烧伤了也很可惜嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.78,0:16:08.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来如此
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.11,0:16:11.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我摧枯拉朽的美貌
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.56,0:16:15.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让你这个色情狂在战斗中满脑子邪恶妄想
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.83,0:16:18.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,导致无法做出正确判断
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.37,0:16:19.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是这么回事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.68,0:16:22.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,摧枯拉朽…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.53,0:16:24.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走吧 王正在等你
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.59,0:16:26.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.74,0:16:29.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪有人会乖乖走过去行刑的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.30,0:16:30.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不来也可以
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.20,0:16:34.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只不过 你一定会悔青了肠子的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.28,0:16:42.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,受不了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.57,0:16:47.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fad(300,0)}{\fs40}罗兰德 城下町
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.13,0:16:54.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这国家到底发生了什么事？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.61,0:17:00.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,欢迎 莱纳
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.96,0:17:02.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,欢迎光临我的宫殿
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.50,0:17:03.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哟
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.49,0:17:10.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我累了 今天先睡了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.57,0:17:11.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,晚安
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.64,0:17:13.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂喂 怎么说也是国王殿前啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.01,0:17:16.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管 我很困
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.35,0:17:19.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说来 觉得他怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.49,0:17:21.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是个超乎想象的色情狂
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.62,0:17:26.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,若置之不理 数年之内必会犯下可怕的罪行
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.43,0:17:27.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.31,0:17:31.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第一次被兄长以外的人手下留情
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.04,0:17:33.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.88,0:17:36.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也适可而止吧 莱纳
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.64,0:17:38.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不然不告诉你姬珐的消息了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.79,0:17:40.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无所谓
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.87,0:17:42.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她死了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.47,0:17:43.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.95,0:17:46.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,骗你的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.89,0:17:48.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你小子…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.28,0:17:51.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姬珐把你托付给我就离开了这个国家
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.04,0:17:54.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说是想四处巡游多看看这个世界
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.54,0:18:00.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过 今天请你来不是为了告诉你这个
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.14,0:18:03.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的报告？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.99,0:18:06.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,“如何建立午睡王国”
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.30,0:18:09.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,标题虽然胡来 内容却着实有趣
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.48,0:18:11.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,传说中的勇者遗物
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.73,0:18:14.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,将那无法衡量的强大威力用作抑制力
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.67,0:18:16.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,消除全世界的战争
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.91,0:18:19.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真厉害 亏你想得出来
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.06,0:18:22.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要随便看人家的报告
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.30,0:18:24.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我很中意这报告
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.98,0:18:28.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因此莱纳
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.64,0:18:30.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你现在立刻去巡游世界
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.87,0:18:33.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把那勇者遗物全部给我收集来
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.78,0:18:35.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊？为啥要我去
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.97,0:18:39.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只不过 光是莱纳去我担心你会偷懒
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.71,0:18:42.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希望菲莉丝作为他的辅佐一起去
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.79,0:18:45.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了世界和平
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.88,0:18:47.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就拜托你们啦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.21,0:18:47.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁要去啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.05,0:18:50.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只是为了打发时间才写了那报告
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.73,0:18:52.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不听我的命令…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.89,0:18:54.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就判死刑
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.80,0:18:55.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呼唤和平啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.82,0:18:57.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在想什么
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.74,0:19:00.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只是受兄长之命才协助你
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.94,0:19:02.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,并不是你的部下
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.09,0:19:05.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,露西尔已经同意了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.73,0:19:06.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,彼曰：
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.16,0:19:11.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,菲莉丝若不听话 就立马拆了维尼特团子店
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.77,0:19:12.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以上
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.03,0:19:17.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,两分钟内启程
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.67,0:19:19.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚才那是什么声音
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.16,0:19:21.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他是来真的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.92,0:19:23.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没时间了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.96,0:19:25.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走了色情狂
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.70,0:19:27.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说没时间了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.30,0:19:28.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,选择题
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.20,0:19:29.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一 丢脑袋
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.43,0:19:30.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,二 丢身体
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.64,0:19:32.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,三 听我的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.68,0:19:33.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,选哪个
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.10,0:19:36.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,席恩你小子给我记着
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.29,0:19:38.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你终于肯去了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.79,0:19:39.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁肯去啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.57,0:19:40.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剩余一分钟
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.38,0:19:43.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都说这声音是啥啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.65,0:19:46.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么 王
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.55,0:19:47.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们走了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.22,0:19:49.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 莱纳交给你了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.59,0:19:51.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们不要随便决定啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.03,0:19:53.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了走吧 搭档
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.56,0:19:55.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁是你搭档啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.55,0:20:00.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,露西尔
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.75,0:20:03.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我所前往的目的地 是这个吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.04,0:20:06.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那也是未来之一
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.96,0:20:09.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个地方并非你的终点
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.69,0:20:11.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我还不会杀了你
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.03,0:20:13.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,王为物
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.23,0:20:14.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是国家的一个齿轮
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.94,0:20:16.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不会破坏新齿轮
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.23,0:20:21.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你还很新呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.05,0:20:23.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我会走我的道路
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.44,0:20:27.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莱纳 你所选择的道路是这条吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.67,0:20:30.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那倒也罢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.18,0:20:32.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然和我相异
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.28,0:20:38.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讨厌人死 也讨厌杀人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.23,0:20:41.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讨厌让人哭 也讨厌哭
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.98,0:20:46.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无可选择的人生 会是怎样心情？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.72,0:20:50.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,失去至亲 失去至爱又如何？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.58,0:20:54.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁也不希望这种事发生
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.66,0:20:59.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知为何世界却总笑着追求这种无意义的悲伤
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.94,0:21:03.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从未想过勉强去改变什么
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.64,0:21:07.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可不改变又很难过
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.43,0:21:09.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也不想再失去任何东西了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.34,0:21:13.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说来麻烦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.13,0:21:15.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,差不多也该向前进了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.09,0:21:18.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然一直故意视而不见
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.57,0:21:19.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但若有必要
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.38,0:21:21.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也会直面自己的过去
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.71,0:21:26.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了创造一个谁也不会再失去任何东西的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.68,0:21:29.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那女孩 姬珐不再哭泣
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.14,0:21:32.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,塔伊尔 托尼 珐露不会死
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.63,0:21:35.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,席恩也不用再自寻烦恼的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.72,0:21:43.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家欢笑着 只要睡睡午觉就好的…世界



Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.63,0:23:23.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,旅行 任务 探索 冒险

Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.22,0:23:26.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇真是烦死了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.37,0:23:28.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,烦到没边
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.18,0:23:30.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,话说啥 这个麻烦的女人还是我搭档
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.83,0:23:34.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂你 慢着 反对暴力…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.98,0:23:34.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fad(300,0)}{\fs40}开始觉醒的世界
